## Branding Requirements (additional conditions)

The following branding conditions apply to any use, modification, redistribution,  
packaging, or republishing of this Software or any derivative work, whether in  
source or binary form:

1. You must preserve the in-app text:  
   **“Provided by Angry Admin”**  
   exactly as written, without alteration.

2. You must include and keep active, visible hyperlinks to:  
   - https://www.angrysysops.com  
   - https://playhackmenow.com  
   - https://buymeacoffee.com/angrysysops  
   - Angry Admin YouTube channel  
   wherever the Software, user interface, or documentation displays such links.

3. You must include this **Branding Requirements** section (or a direct link to it)  
   in any redistributed README file, documentation bundle, installer, download  
   page, package description, or any distribution channel where the Software  
   is made available.

4. You must reproduce the following author credit clearly and prominently:  
   **Piotr Tarnawski (Angry Admin) — @TheTechWorldPod**

